<br>
I would advise against this idea of just going to 1 plane to &quot;learn the ropes&quot;.  If your posting here asking us if you look greedy, I suspect your conscience is already nagging you.  This sounds like a justification to me and your asking for our stamp of approval.<br>
<br>
When I was up and coming my first 8 planes raids were, 1 hate and 7 fear.  Why?  I found hate to be extremely dull.  It was to easy!  Fear on the other hand was a challenge to be conquered.  The break had gotten us several times.  There was real risk and real sense of accomplishment if you succeeded ( at least in the break ).  <br>
<br>
