<br>
Do whatever you find fun.<br>
<br>
Akbar <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/uakbarbelakesh.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Akbar BelAkesh</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0> at: 8/7/01 1:39:08 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#E5E5E6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/uillithsidmistwalker.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Illithsid Mistwalker</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>p0\/\/3r-p0sT3r!</span><br> <font color=#000033>(8/7/01 1:49:28 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Looking for advice</span><hr size=1> Hehe Llorian, I do that all the time. <br>
